					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Would it be possible, with timed code or a custom mapper, to switch name tables half-way through each scan-line?  So that the left side of the screen comes from one name table, and the right side comes from the other?  Then any graphics that would need to extend over the boundary would be done with sprite overlays?
<br />
<br />I'm not an expert here.  I'm just proposing an idea.  However, I am unsure if it would work.  I seem to remember that to stay in the same pixel column on the screen, but drop down one row, the game would need to delay a fractional count of cpu cycles.</div>

